      • export

        public void export(io.springlets.data.domain.GlobalSearch search,
                   @PageableDefault(size=2147483647)
                   org.springframework.data.domain.Pageable pageable,
                   String[] datatablesColumns,
                   javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response,
                   JasperReportsExporter exporter,
                   String fileName,
                   Locale locale)

        Method that obtains the filtered and ordered records using the Datatables information and export them to a new report file. (It ignores the current pagination).

        To generate the report file it uses the DynamicJasper library (http://dynamicjasper.com). This library allows developers to generate reports dynamically without use an specific template to each entity.

        To customize the appearance of ALL generated reports, you could customize the "export_default.jrxml" template located in "src/main/resources/templates/reports/". However, if you want to customize the appearance of this specific report, you could create a new ".jrxml" file and provide it to the library replacing the builder.setTemplateFile(); operation used in this implementation.

        パラメータ:
        search - GlobalSearch that contains the filter provided by the Datatables component.
        pageable - Pageable that contains the Sort info provided by the Datatabes component.
        datatablesColumns - Columns displayed in the Datatables component.
        response - The HttpServletResponse.
        exporter - An specific JasperReportsExporter to be used during export process.
        fileName - The final filename to use.
        locale - The current Locale in the view context.

      • addColumnToReportBuilder

        public void addColumnToReportBuilder(String columnName,
                                     ar.com.fdvs.dj.domain.builders.FastReportBuilder builder,
                                     Locale locale,
                                     String fileName)

        This method contains all the entity fields that are able to be displayed in a report. The developer could add a new column to the report builder providing the field name and the builder where the new field will be added as column.

        パラメータ:
        columnName - the field name to show as column
        builder - The builder where the new field will be added as column.
